 in previous studies, with a more evolved, diffuse central region,\nand a younger, more compact southern region. However, the local PDR conditions\nare averaged out on the 175 pc scales that we probe and do not reflect\ndifferences observed in the star formation properties of the two regions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 22 Jun 2015 20:28:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-19"}
